{T=FTcts_13/C=0xFFA62700/}[Details]{T=QTtext/C=0xFF4D0D08/}
Key is needed to enter the Aries Dungeon. If you talk to Crete, she will give you Bracelet of the Twins, which can be used to enter Aries. Talk to Crete.

